'''Pat Paris''' is an artist who illustrated several children's books and other works featuring [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]].<ref name="SWI 74">{{InsiderCite|74|Wasaka Berries and Monster Ships: Star Wars Storybook 101}}</ref> Paris was responsible for much of [[Lucasfilm]]'s "cute Ewok" art found in books and other materials in [[1983]] and [[1984]], before later works began to be more directly inspired by the ''[[Ewoks (television series)|Ewoks]]'' animated series.<ref name="Galaxy 3">{{Topps|set=1995 Topps Star Wars Galaxy Series 3|cardname=''Wicket Finds a Way'' (299)|link=https://www.tcdb.com/ViewCard.cfm/sid/75145/cid/6267008?PageIndex=1}}</ref>

